# LTP Publisher Public Key (Ed25519)
# Used to verify signatures on LTP drop JSON files.
# The corresponding private key lives on the VPS only — never committed to git.
#
# To verify a drop signature, use this key with the Ed25519 algorithm
# against the canonical JSON payload (sorted keys, no whitespace).
#
-----BEGIN PUBLIC KEY-----
MCowBQYDK2VwAyEAMtpeQ7Gae3YUwzUVjh2fyToF/oGi2OBWUWipXia0BeM=
-----END PUBLIC KEY-----
